#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&atlantik; is a client for playing &Monopoly;-like board games on the "
"&monopd; network."
msgstr ""
"&atlantik; es un cliente para juegos similares a &Monopoly; en la red "
"&monopd;."

